<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<lcui-app>
  <ui>
    <w type="rate-view" class="view">
      <w type="h1">Rate</w>
<w type="p">Rate component can be used to show evaluation, and it provide a quick rating operation on something.</w>
<w type="h2">Basic</w>
<w type="p">The simplest usage.</w>

<w class="demo-box rate-basic-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><rate /></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="h2">Readonly</w>
<w type="p">Set the [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] disabled [/bgcolor][/color] attribute to disable mouse interaction.</w>

<w class="demo-box rate-readonly-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><rate value="2" disabled="disabled" /></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]value=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;2&quot;[/color] [color=#4070a0]disabled=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;disabled&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="h2">Other star count</w>
<w type="p">The default number of stars is 5, you can set it with the [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] count [/bgcolor][/color] attribute.</w>

<w class="demo-box rate-count-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><rate count="10" /></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]count=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;10&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="h2">Other icon</w>
<w type="p">Replace the default star to other iconfont.</w>

<w class="demo-box rate-icon-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><rate icon="heart" void-icon="heart-outline" />
<w class="mb-2" />
<rate icon="emoticon-happy" void-icon="emoticon-neutral-outline" /></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]icon=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;heart&quot;[/color] [color=#4070a0]void-icon=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;heart-outline&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;w[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;mb-2&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]icon=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;emoticon-happy&quot;[/color] [color=#4070a0]void-icon=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;emoticon-neutral-outline&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>
<w type="h2">Other character</w>
<w type="p">Replace the default star to other character like alphabet, digit or even Chinese word.</w>

<w class="demo-box rate-character-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><rate character="A" />
<w class="mb-2" />
<rate character="好" /></w>
  <w type="code-block" class="code-block">[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]character=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;A&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;w[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]class=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;mb-2&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]
[color=#062873][b]&lt;rate[/color][/b] [color=#4070a0]character=[/color][color=#a31515]&quot;好&quot;[/color] [color=#062873][b]/&gt;[/color][/b]</w>
</w>

    </w>
  </ui>
</lcui-app>
